PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR, namely the Hon. A. KERR TWADDLE, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Manitoba, who shall temporarily execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of MANITOBA for the duration of the period extending from November 18 to November 19, 1993.
